WEBVTT

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:01.440
and fell asleep.

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:03.856
And when I woke up,

00:03:03.880 --> 00:03:08.800
I saw my daughter
drizzling sand on her arm like this,

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:15.016
and I could feel that light tickle
of sand on her skin

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:17.520
and I remembered my aunt brushing my hair.

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:20.736
So I curled up next to her

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:24.240
and I drizzled sand on her other arm
and then her legs.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:28.400
And then I said,
"Hey, you want me to bury you?"

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.776
And her eyes got really big
and she was like, "Yeah!"